library(ggplot2)

chrom_wid <- 0.05
chrom_offset <- 0.2

p <- ggplot2::ggplot()
p <- p + theme_bw()
p <- p + ggplot2::geom_rect( 
  data = EH23a, 
  ggplot2::aes( xmin = chrom_num - chrom_wid - chrom_offset,
                xmax = chrom_num + chrom_wid - chrom_offset,
                ymin = 1, ymax = Length),
  fill = "#DCDCDC",
  color = "#000000"
)
